{"tid":1846840,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【仲考慮緊罷工既醫護入一入黎】睇張圖你就知點揀","createTime":"2020-01-27T18:08:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T02:26:28.000Z","uid":290207,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"689a83e674b174debf61aa52e2aa591cc777cdd4","tid":1846840,"uid":290207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:08:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rwKqy4R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrwKqy4R.png&h=f47ae408&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔洗解釋，一目了然。<br />\n<br />\n非常時期，唔好講話跟遊戲規則玩。<br />\n<br />\n2月3號罷工已經太撚遲，你同無賴玩遊戲，你輸鳩梗。<br />\n<br />\n你教既唔撚係香港人，係情緒勒索你地既港共。<br />\n<br />\n你地講一句罷工<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地全香港人陪你地一齊罷</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔該同我上熱門。"},{"pid":"fa974758f43d78cb259bd13c8f582beff034424c","tid":1846840,"uid":100422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:14:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9329c4e8b750d70c019f1d367316007bbea38533","tid":1846840,"uid":100422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:14:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61ec6611c547ad1627f382aec03ee82da2169157","tid":1846840,"uid":100422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:15:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f45fadb72c8dac5b611d0162e3d451834482cd97","tid":1846840,"uid":100422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45bff2b34e8d1aea6f532461fe2bc4e02e598de9","tid":1846840,"uid":326195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:15:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac